    <div data-cid="1433257">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1433257">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/coffeeland/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img9.doubanio.com/icon/u1130861-106.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/coffeeland/" class="name">毛利</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2008-07-09" class="main-meta">2008-07-09 11:29:49</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1433257/">怎么像他一样红？</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1433257_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1433257">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        07年某天我在广州火车站附近转悠，买点吃的喝的报纸杂志，准备拿来度过20小时的硬座火车休闲时光。当我路过N个书报摊小书店，发现每一家门口都摆着《明朝那些事儿》，简直有如燎原之势，走过第一家的时候我想，不能买不能买，买畅销书就没品位，买网络畅销书带回家都不好意思，...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1433257-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1433257_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1433257_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1433257" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1433257">
                                696
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1433257" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1433257">
                                76
